      "writtenOn": "2018-11-06T15:33:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If we immediately delete, then the 0 won\u0027t be sent to Prometheus, so the old value sticks around. If the previous value was causing an alert, the alert will stay active indefinitely. I could try to figure out how to delete it after the next cycle, but IMO the severity of this leak is pretty small.",
      "parentUuid": "49e4d91f_263a79d7",
